relation: Share any unusual traditions or locations on campus
Security is always around and it feels comfortable to walk to your car even after night classes.
They always have something fun happening in the Cougar Grille and celebrate holidays in style with all sorts of fun activities available.

The Cougar Grille is a little tiny and people sit there whether they are eating or not but if you do get the chance to sit down and eat a meal it is comfortable and the food is good. Get the pizza!!!!
There are no on campus dorms at this facility.
Use your resources that are available to you. Use the counseling office and find out who your advisor is and talk to them on a regular basis.
FCC has a great selection of classes to choose from. They help you figure out what you want to do with your life and set you on a complete track to obtain a degree.
